你做过的事情, 已经不能回头了

6
00:00:21,113 --> 00:00:22,554
You have to tell me the truth.
你必须得跟我说实话

7
00:00:23,112 --> 00:00:25,137
- You don't understand.  - Try me.
- 你不会明白的  - 试试

8
00:00:36,931 --> 00:00:39,406
No, I don't feel in control.
不, 我觉得我有控制权

9
00:00:41,271 --> 00:00:42,271
I feel old.
我觉得老了

10
00:00:44,102 --> 00:00:46,753
- You're not safe here.
- I'm not safe anywhere.
- 你在这里不安全  - 我在哪里都不安全

11
00:00:46,825 --> 00:00:49,105
- Shall we go back, then?
- Natasha.
- 那, 我们该回去吗？  - Natasha

12
00:00:49,135 --> 00:00:51,842
Whatever happened on Sentinel Island isn't over.
不管哨兵岛上发生的是什么, 都还没有结束

13
00:00:52,286 --> 00:00:55,065
You're part of it now, Lockwood.
It's part of you.
你现在是它的一部分了, Lockwood．它也是你的一部分

14
00:00:55,090 --> 00:00:58,261
It's for that very reason, I can't go back.
正是因为这个原因, 我才不能回去

15
00:00:59,425 --> 00:01:02,802
How long do you think my head would
stay connected to the rest of my body?
你觉得我的脑袋还能跟我身体的其它部位一起待多久？

16
00:01:02,827 --> 00:01:03,508
But UNIT wouldn't...
但 UNIT 不会...

17
00:01:03,633 --> 00:01:07,720
There are fairies at the bottom
of my garden too.
在我的花园底部也有很多小仙子

18
00:01:10,446 --> 00:01:11,155
You're right.
你说得对

19
00:01:12,609 --> 00:01:14,568
I tried to contain that thing...
我试图笼住那个东西...

20
00:01:16,287 --> 00:01:16,834
Here.
这里

21
00:01:17,933 --> 00:01:19,933
But all I did was give it a route back.
但我所做的事情其实是给了它一条路

22
00:01:20,562 --> 00:01:22,502
All the more reason
why you should come with me.
那你就更应该跟我来了

23
00:01:23,031 --> 00:01:24,909
I've made a terrible mistake.
我犯了一个严重的错误

24
00:01:26,246 --> 00:01:26,768
Lockwood?
Lockwood?﻿

25
00:02:13,415 --> 00:02:14,853
Mister Winslet.
Winslet 先生

26
00:02:16,019 --> 00:02:17,496
Mister Winslet?
Winslet 先生?

27
00:02:18,962 --> 00:02:19,939
Graham?
Graham?﻿

28
00:02:21,679 --> 00:02:24,450
What are we doing out here
in our jim-jams again?
我们在外面做什么?fixme

29
00:02:30,551 --> 00:02:31,590
Come along.
快过来

30
00:03:09,249 --> 00:03:09,679
No.
不

31
00:03:12,162 --> 00:03:12,948
No.
不

32
00:03:15,050 --> 00:03:16,050
It's coming back.
它回来了

33
00:03:18,010 --> 00:03:19,230
It's coming back for me.
它回来找我了

34
00:03:20,283 --> 00:03:20,983
No.
不

35
00:03:21,911 --> 00:03:22,655
No.
不

36
00:04:00,942 --> 00:04:02,042
Thank you, Dalby.
谢谢你, Dalby

37
00:04:07,233 --> 00:04:09,009
Sit down, Doctor Arnold.
坐下, Arnold 博士

38
00:04:14,540 --> 00:04:15,897
My name is Palmer.
我的名字是 Palmer

39
00:04:16,223 --> 00:04:18,223
You are in my custody now.
你现在在我的监管之下了

40
00:04:18,745 --> 00:04:20,618
A lot's been happening,
Doctor Arnold.
发生了很多事情, Arnold 博士

41
00:04:20,643 --> 00:04:21,421
Catch up.
补补课吧

42
00:04:21,456 --> 00:04:24,486
New York Stock Exchange, 
all systems wiped.
纽约证券交易所, 所有系统被抹掉了

43
00:04:24,533 --> 00:04:26,093
NASDAQ's in free-fall.
纳斯达克在自由落体

44
00:04:26,121 --> 00:04:30,678
Aeroflot flight 496 fell out of the sky
over Berlin, computer malfunction.
Aeroflot 的 496 航班在柏林上空飞出了天外, 电脑故障

45
00:04:31,054 --> 00:04:34,027
Perth Australia, sixteen patients
in intensive care,
澳大利亚珀斯, 16 个病人进入重症监护

46
00:04:34,205 --> 00:04:37,723
their respirators just happened to
turn themselves off at the same time.
他们的呼吸机停掉了，在同一时刻

47
00:04:38,354 --> 00:04:39,563
Just what does this have to do with me?
这些跟我有什么关系

48
00:04:39,953 --> 00:04:43,442
It started when Lockwood left Sentinel Island...
这都是在 Lockwood 离开哨兵岛的时候开始的

49
00:04:45,005 --> 00:04:46,586
