而且还没有停止

50
00:04:47,894 --> 00:04:48,922
In fact, it's getting worse.
事实上, 还在恶化

51
00:04:48,947 --> 00:04:51,097
By the middle of next week 
there won't be a computer left...
到下周中期, 就一台电脑也不剩了...

52
00:04:51,122 --> 00:04:52,922
on the planet that hasn't malfunctioned.
全球的电脑全部都会工作不正常

53
00:04:53,296 --> 00:04:57,190
And that doesn't even scratch the
surface of what's happening at Millhampton.
而这些跟 Millhampton 医院发生的事情比起来都是小巫见大巫

54
00:04:59,347 --> 00:05:02,314
Are we smelling the coffee yet,
Doctor Arnold?
闻到烧咖啡的味道了吗，Arnold 博士？

55
00:05:03,904 --> 00:05:04,706
Look what I found.
看看我找到了什么？

56
00:05:06,539 --> 00:05:07,976
I thought it was best to let you sleep.
我一直觉得最好是让你睡觉

57
00:05:08,022 --> 00:05:09,793
Yeah, sleep.
是啊, 睡觉

58
00:05:10,325 --> 00:05:11,217
Dreams.
做梦

59
00:05:12,224 --> 00:05:13,174
No, thank you.
不了, 谢谢你

60
00:05:13,872 --> 00:05:16,815
I've got enough rubbish inside me
as it is without adding to it.
我体内已经有够多的垃圾了，不需要再加

61
00:05:17,593 --> 00:05:18,629
It's out of you now.
它没在你里面了

62
00:05:20,478 --> 00:05:22,149
Let's take stock, shall we?
我们来捋一下，好吗？

63
00:05:23,585 --> 00:05:25,419
An ancient elemental force...
一股古老的自然力量...

64
00:05:25,592 --> 00:05:27,285
Buried deep below the surface...
深埋在地表之下...

65
00:05:28,221 --> 00:05:30,467
Waiting for a signal to re-emerge.
等着一个信号以东山再起

66
00:05:32,038 --> 00:05:34,038
A paranoid and secretive...
一个偏执而秘密的...

67
00:05:34,133 --> 00:05:36,273
Governmental paramilitary team...
政府半军事化小组...

68
00:05:36,594 --> 00:05:38,304
Desperate to get its hands on me...
不顾一切地想要把我抓到手...

69
00:05:38,692 --> 00:05:39,235
Well...
好吧...

70
00:05:39,901 --> 00:05:41,097
What's inside me,
要的是在我体内的东西

71
00:05:41,121 --> 00:05:42,352
before the enemy does.
抢在敌人之前

72
00:05:43,312 --> 00:05:44,399
How am I doing so far?
我都做了些什么？

73
00:05:45,053 --> 00:05:47,875
UNIT, the Nestenes, 
I bet you never felt so popular.
又是 UNIT, 又是 Nestenes，我打赌你从未觉得如此受欢迎

74
00:05:53,092 --> 00:05:56,490
Someone cut through the wrong cable
at the psychic exchange?
你们的通灵渠道被人切错电缆了？

75
00:05:57,636 --> 00:05:59,260
Try something a little  more...
试试别的方法，比如更加...

76
00:05:59,466 --> 00:06:00,276
Conventional.
传统的

77
00:06:02,059 --> 00:06:03,188
No, wait.
不, 等等

78
00:06:04,696 --> 00:06:05,460
There is something.
这里有事情

79
00:06:08,388 --> 00:06:09,299
Friends.
朋友

80
00:06:10,380 --> 00:06:13,309
Lockwood left the door 
open for them, Doctor Arnold.
Lockwood 给他们留了门, Arnold 博士

81
00:06:14,594 --> 00:06:17,015
Just when was it
you realised he'd changed sides?
你是什么时候发现他改变立场了？

82
00:06:19,436 --> 00:06:22,080
Just before I was 
dragged off by the ISD.
就在我被内部安全部拖出来的时候

83
00:06:27,500 --> 00:06:28,560
You need me.
你需要我

84
00:06:30,828 --> 00:06:32,099
Why should I help you,
我为什么要帮你,

85
00:06:32,123 --> 00:06:34,285
when I've been wired up 
in that dungeon of delights,
我被绑在那个地牢里

86
00:06:34,349 --> 00:06:35,848
interrogated for three weeks solid?
被审讯了整整三个星期？

87
00:06:35,956 --> 00:06:38,448
You're a close associate of Lockwood's.
你是 Lockwood 关系紧密的同事

88
00:06:40,129 --> 00:06:41,250
Now, the question is...
现在的问题是...

89
00:06:41,710 --> 00:06:43,585
Just how close?
有多紧密？

90
00:06:44,545 --> 00:06:45,606
What do you want from me?
你想从我这里得到什么？

91
00:06:53,385 --> 00:06:54,613
When we last met...
上次我们碰面的时候...

92
00:06:55,334 --> 00:06:57,334
a seed was planted in your mind.
就将一颗种子种在了你的意识里

93
00:06:58,715 --> 00:06:59,292
Your very...
你那非常..

94
00:07:00,276 --> 00:07:02,231
Very special mind, Lockwood.
非常特别的意识，Lockwood

95
00:07:02,758 --> 00:07:04,578
You're too kind.
你太好心了

96
00:07:05,914 --> 00:07:06,886
It's been...
它一直在...

97
00:07:08,346 --> 00:07:09,299
Germinating.
发芽...

98
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:13,894
Why are you investigating Lockwood?
你为什么在调查 Lockwood?

99
00:07:14,282 --> 00:07:15,884
He's UNIT's best operative.
他是 UNIT 最好的特工

100
00:07:16,836 --> 00:07:19,225
We're investigating him because his...
我们调查他是因为他的...

101
00:07:19,519 --> 00:07:21,084
special abilities...
特殊能力...

102
00:07:21,290 --> 00:07:22,695
are a two-way street.
那是一条双行道

103
00:07:23,582 --> 00:07:25,017
He may have permanent access...
他可能有永久权限...

104
00:07:25,041 --> 00:07:26,948
to the sum total of 
UNIT's acquired wisdom...
可以访问 UNIT 所获取的所有智慧...

105
00:07:27,408 --> 00:07:29,032
through a piece of hardware in his brain,
仅仅通过他大脑里的一小片硬件fixme

106
00:07:29,573 --> 00:07:32,426
but that means someone, 
somewhere in this great organisation...
但这就意味着某个人，在这个大机构里面某个地方...

107
00:07:32,550 --> 00:07:34,276
is watching over his every thought.
在观察着他的每一个想法

108
00:07:38,798 --> 00:07:40,903
Now listen to me, you stubborn old bastard.
听我说，你个顽固的老东西

109
00:07:41,305 --> 00:07:44,458
Don't let that smooth-talking piece 
of plastic let you wallow in self-pity.
别让那个巧舌如簧的塑料假人, 引导你沉溺于自怜中

110
00:07:44,830 --> 00:07:46,401
Look into my mind.
进入我的意识看看

111
00:07:47,048 --> 00:07:48,908
I know what it's like to be the outsider...
我知道当一个局外人是什么样的...

112
00:07:49,055 --> 00:07:51,140
But we make ourselves outsiders.
但那是我们自己让自己成为局外人

113
00:07:51,410 --> 00:07:53,410
The trick is to let people in.
关键是要让别人进来

114
00:07:53,735 --> 00:07:55,435
Lockwood, I'm letting you in.
Lockwood，我让你进来

115
00:07:59,821 --> 00:08:00,871
Where did that creature go?
那个生物去了哪里？

116
00:08:02,612 --> 00:08:03,812
It hasn't gone, has it.
它还没走，是吧？

117
00:08:03,836 --> 00:08:05,089
Lockwood, what have you done?
Lockwood，你做了什么？

118
00:08:06,700 --> 00:08:08,000
Whose side are you on?
你到底是哪边的？

119
00:08:16,233 --> 00:08:17,783
So you're psychic too.
看来你也是个通灵者

120
00:08:18,410 --> 00:08:19,646
You read Natasha's mind.
你读了 Natasha 的思想

121
00:08:20,700 --> 00:08:21,429
What did she mean?
她是什么意思

122
00:08:22,620 --> 00:08:24,499
From what you're showing me,
Lockwood destroyed the thing.
从你显示给我的东西来看，Lockwood 摧毁了那个东西

123
00:08:24,524 --> 00:08:27,067
Not destroyed, absorbed.
不是摧毁，是吸收了

124
00:08:28,297 --> 00:08:29,305
