when they got back to the mainland?
那他们回到大陆之后，Millhampton 医院发生了什么？

127
00:08:33,652 --> 00:08:34,657
We don't know.
我们不知道

128
00:08:36,732 --> 00:08:38,574
You've lost contact with Natasha.
你跟 Natasha 失去联系了

129
00:08:40,137 --> 00:08:41,001
And Lockwood.
跟 Lockwood 也是

130
00:08:41,172 --> 00:08:42,422
You...
你...

131
00:08:42,794 --> 00:08:44,010
care for him.
关心他

132
00:08:48,213 --> 00:08:48,918
Yes.
是的

133
00:08:49,037 --> 00:08:50,267
Then help me.
那就帮我

134
00:08:52,317 --> 00:08:53,857
Millhampton hospital.
Millhampton 医院

135
00:08:54,484 --> 00:08:56,284
- Are you sure?  - Yes.
- 你确定吗？  - 是的

136
00:08:57,522 --> 00:08:58,237
They're here.
他们在这里

137
00:08:58,798 --> 00:08:59,428
Ramsay?
Ramsay吗?

138
00:08:59,817 --> 00:09:01,817
- The team?  - No.
- 他的小组？  - 不是

139
00:09:03,801 --> 00:09:04,448
Them.
是他们

140
00:09:07,219 --> 00:09:09,209
The psychiatric unit.
精神科

141
00:09:10,030 --> 00:09:11,210
Of course.
当然了

142
00:09:12,282 --> 00:09:14,901
This is where we sent the 
real Winslet to recuperate.
我们把真正的 Winslet 送到这里来调理

143
00:09:16,638 --> 00:09:17,737
Clever bastards.
聪明的混蛋

144
00:09:27,821 --> 00:09:29,880
Even you, Miss Alexander?
就连你，Alexander 小姐？

145
00:09:31,958 --> 00:09:35,030
No one else could have kept me
as effectively hidden from UNIT
没有其他人可以把我如此有效地藏起来躲过UNIT

146
00:09:35,055 --> 00:09:37,953
and be reeled in without even noticing.
被耍得团团转而浑然不觉

147
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:46,010
I was always the last boy
picked at games.
玩游戏时我总是最后一个被挑中的

148
00:09:47,663 --> 00:09:48,893
Nothing changes.
什么都没变

149
00:09:53,835 --> 00:09:55,935
If I can't get out...
如果我出不去...

150
00:09:55,959 --> 00:09:58,068
then I'm not going to let you in!
你我也不打算让你们进去！

151
00:10:04,175 --> 00:10:05,458
Time to sleep.
睡觉时间到了

152
00:10:08,050 --> 00:10:09,163
To sleep.
该睡觉了

153
00:10:11,616 --> 00:10:12,616
To dream.
做梦

154
00:11:21,011 --> 00:11:22,122
Transmission cut out.
信号传输被切断了

155
00:11:22,185 --> 00:11:22,918
Damn it.
该死

156
00:11:23,354 --> 00:11:25,254
What did Palmer have to say,
anything useful?
Palmer 有什么要说的，有什么有用的吗？

157
00:11:25,491 --> 00:11:27,874
Only the air contact was normal on
the west side of the town.
只说了镇子西边的空中联络还正常

158
00:12:22,047 --> 00:12:23,217
Run for it!
快跑！

159
00:13:39,409 --> 00:13:40,403
Open fire.
开火

160
00:14:02,716 --> 00:14:03,964
Not quite what I expected.
跟我料想的不太一样

161
00:14:05,035 --> 00:14:07,035
Nice to know all my research
paid off, though.
不过，知道自己的研究有价值，真好

162
00:14:15,544 --> 00:14:17,968
- Come on, Sal.
- Just a minute. Power surge.
- 快点，Sal   - 等一下，能量涌动

163
00:14:38,353 --> 00:14:39,913
Greyhound One to Greyhound Leader.
灰狗一号呼叫灰狗队长

164
00:14:41,214 --> 00:14:42,548
Palmer, it's Ramsay.
Palmer, 我是 Ramsay.

165
00:14:42,982 --> 00:14:44,249
We need rein...
我们需要增...

166
00:15:33,015 --> 00:15:34,362
Looks like they've cranked up the power.
看来他们已经增强了能量

167
00:15:36,983 --> 00:15:39,188
Run for it... Run for it, Sal!
快跑...跑啊，Sal！

168
00:16:19,980 --> 00:16:20,910
Natasha? 
Natasha?﻿

169
00:16:21,941 --> 00:16:23,595
Ah, more dreams.
啊，又是梦

170
00:16:25,018 --> 00:16:27,231
Amazing what goes on in the mind...
脑海里会发生什么，让人惊讶啊

171
00:16:29,429 --> 00:16:30,860
At the point of death.
在此濒临死亡之时

172
00:16:34,902 --> 00:16:36,062
Lockwood, wake up.
Lockwood，醒醒

173
00:16:36,165 --> 00:16:37,522
We've got to get out of here.
我们必须得离开这里

174
00:16:47,695 --> 00:16:49,053
You don't remember what happened.
你不记得发生了什么

175
00:16:53,537 --> 00:16:54,804
Lockwood, please.
Lockwood，求你了

176
00:16:55,188 --> 00:16:56,864
You can't distract me.
你没法分散我的注意力

177
00:16:57,268 --> 00:16:58,419
You're only a dream.
你只是一个梦

178
00:17:01,914 --> 00:17:04,070
I wonder who else I shall dream about?
我好奇我还会梦到谁？

179
00:17:18,974 --> 00:17:22,121
Oh, Palmer. Have you seen Ramsay?
噢，Palmer。你见到 Ramsay 了吗？

180
00:17:24,408 --> 00:17:25,620
What about the rest of your team?
你小组的其他人呢？

181
00:17:28,450 --> 00:17:30,326
Oh, running behind schedule, are we?
噢，我们落后于原定计划了，是吧？

182
00:17:31,508 --> 00:17:33,395
Got to find Lockwood.
去找到 Lockwood

183
00:17:33,419 --> 00:17:35,035
That's what we're here for, isn't it?
那是我们到这里来的原因，是吧？

184
00:17:35,060 --> 00:17:36,623
Look, you asked me to help you...
看，你请求我帮助你...

185
